*In May 2013, Parkison was the keynote speaker of the Association of Carolina Emerging Scholars Conference at USC Lancaster<ref>{{cite web|title=Association of Carolina Emerging Scholars|url=http://usclancaster.sc.edu/cesc/2013/speakers/index.html|publisher=University of South Carolina}}</ref>

